title: TWIN vs TWIN Underwater Photo Competition ft/ Brooklyn & Bailey
author: Jordan Matter
description:
I've been waiting THREE YEARS to work with twin queens Brooklyn & Bailey! This is my most epic underwater competition yet, and the winner gets a HUGE PRIZE! Kamri Noel inspired me to become an underwater photographer, and today she challenges me to see who can take the best photos! Wait until the end for a surprise announcement 😱
